summary: Snow Elf Home located in the Reach in the mountains behind Bthardamz. Features all the crafting stations, storage and displays. Room for 3 Followers. Not a large home, but not exactly small either.
descriptionHtml:
[color=#a4c2f4][size=6]Snow Elf Hut[/size][/color]

[img]https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/77198-0-1468901824.jpg[/img]

Snow Elf themed home Located in the Reach in the mountains behind Bthardamz (See map in the image section)
Must be purchased for 7,500 gold - Click the sale sign at the door

[color=#e06666]Requires all DLC's[/color]

[img]https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/77198-0-1468904022.png[/img]

[youtube]BdZPawdKrPg[/youtube] [youtube]uHvDpsE7SZU[/youtube]

[color=#f6b26b][size=4]Features[/size][/color]
4 Levels (See layout image in the image section)
Level 1 - Kitchen, Dining & Alchemy/Enchanting
Level 2 - Library
Level 3 - Displays
Level 4 - Master Bedroom, Follower Room (3 beds) & Pool

Custom Elf follower
Auto undressing for NPC's at pools
Teleport Spell

[color=#f6b26b][size=4]Recommended mods[/size][/color]
